  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Occupational Therapist / Hand Therapist",
  "description": "<p><strong>🚀 Join Our Team as a Senior Occupational Therapist / Hand Therapist!</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Heartland Rehab is expanding, and we’re looking for a <strong>Senior Occupational Therapist / Hand Therapist</strong> to join our growing team! If you’re passionate about <strong>helping clients regain hand function and independence</strong>, we want to hear from you.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🔹 About the Role:</strong></p>\n<p>✅ Provide expert care in hand therapy and rehabilitation</p>\n<p>✅ Develop and implement personalized treatment plans</p>\n<p>✅ Work collaboratively in a <strong>team built on trust and teamwork</strong></p>\n<p>✅ Enjoy <strong>flexible hours</strong> with a <strong>competitive base pay + commission</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🔹 What We’re Looking For:</strong></p>\n<p>✔️ <strong>Bachelor’s Degree in Occupational Therapy</strong></p>\n<p>✔️ <strong>At least 3 years of OT experience</strong></p>\n<p>✔️ Experience in <strong>hand therapy</strong> (Hand Therapy Certification preferred)</p>\n<p>✔️ Outgoing, team-oriented professional</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🔹 What We Offer:</strong></p>\n<p>💰 Competitive <strong>base salary + commission</strong></p>\n<p>⏳ <strong>Flexible working hours</strong></p>\n<p>📚 <strong>Training funds</strong> to support your professional growth</p>\n<p>📈 Be part of a <strong>growing and dynamic team</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to take your career to the next level?</strong> Send your CV to <strong>jobs@heartlandrehab.sg</strong> and join us in making a difference! 💙💪</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>#OccupationalTherapist #HandTherapist #CareerGrowth #HealthcareJobs #JoinOurTeam</p>",
